name: @tinijs/icons
description: The icon packages of the TiniJS framework.
author: Lam Nhan

scripts.build: npm run build:1:bootstrap && npm run build:2:material-filled && npm run build:3:material-outlined && npm run build:4:material-round && npm run build:5:material-sharp && npm run build:6:material-two-tone && npm run build:7:mdi && npm run build:8:ionic && npm run build:9:fluent && npm run build:10:ant-filled && npm run build:11:ant-outlined && npm run build:12:ant-twotone && npm run build:13:fontawesome-brands && npm run build:14:fontawesome-regular && npm run build:15:fontawesome-solid
scripts.build:1:bootstrap: tini ui icon @tinijs/bootstrap-icons _/bootstrap-icons/icons && parcel build build/@tinijs/bootstrap-icons/*.bundle.ts --dist-dir build/@tinijs/bootstrap-icons --no-cache --no-source-maps --log-level warn
scripts.build:2:material-filled: tini ui icon @tinijs/material-filled-icons _/@material-design-icons/svg/filled && parcel build build/@tinijs/material-filled-icons/*.bundle.ts --dist-dir build/@tinijs/material-filled-icons --no-cache --no-source-maps --log-level warn
scripts.build:3:material-outlined: tini ui icon @tinijs/material-outlined-icons _/@material-design-icons/svg/outlined && parcel build build/@tinijs/material-outlined-icons/*.bundle.ts --dist-dir build/@tinijs/material-outlined-icons --no-cache --no-source-maps --log-level warn
scripts.build:4:material-round: tini ui icon @tinijs/material-round-icons _/@material-design-icons/svg/round && parcel build build/@tinijs/material-round-icons/*.bundle.ts --dist-dir build/@tinijs/material-round-icons --no-cache --no-source-maps --log-level warn
scripts.build:5:material-sharp: tini ui icon @tinijs/material-sharp-icons _/@material-design-icons/svg/sharp && parcel build build/@tinijs/material-sharp-icons/*.bundle.ts --dist-dir build/@tinijs/material-sharp-icons --no-cache --no-source-maps --log-level warn
scripts.build:6:material-two-tone: tini ui icon @tinijs/material-two-tone-icons _/@material-design-icons/svg/two-tone && parcel build build/@tinijs/material-two-tone-icons/*.bundle.ts --dist-dir build/@tinijs/material-two-tone-icons --no-cache --no-source-maps --log-level warn
scripts.build:7:mdi: tini ui icon @tinijs/mdi-icons _/@mdi/svg/svg && parcel build build/@tinijs/mdi-icons/*.bundle.ts --dist-dir build/@tinijs/mdi-icons --no-cache --no-source-maps --log-level warn
scripts.build:8:ionic: tini ui icon @tinijs/ionic-icons _/ionicons/dist/svg && parcel build build/@tinijs/ionic-icons/*.bundle.ts --dist-dir build/@tinijs/ionic-icons --no-cache --no-source-maps --log-level warn
scripts.build:9:fluent: tini ui icon @tinijs/fluent-icons _/@fluentui/svg-icons/icons && parcel build build/@tinijs/fluent-icons/*.bundle.ts --dist-dir build/@tinijs/fluent-icons --no-cache --no-source-maps --log-level warn
scripts.build:10:ant-filled: tini ui icon @tinijs/ant-filled-icons _/@ant-design/icons-svg/inline-namespaced-svg/filled && parcel build build/@tinijs/ant-filled-icons/*.bundle.ts --dist-dir build/@tinijs/ant-filled-icons --no-cache --no-source-maps --log-level warn
scripts.build:11:ant-outlined: tini ui icon @tinijs/ant-outlined-icons _/@ant-design/icons-svg/inline-namespaced-svg/outlined && parcel build build/@tinijs/ant-outlined-icons/*.bundle.ts --dist-dir build/@tinijs/ant-outlined-icons --no-cache --no-source-maps --log-level warn
scripts.build:12:ant-twotone: tini ui icon @tinijs/ant-twotone-icons _/@ant-design/icons-svg/inline-namespaced-svg/twotone && parcel build build/@tinijs/ant-twotone-icons/*.bundle.ts --dist-dir build/@tinijs/ant-twotone-icons --no-cache --no-source-maps --log-level warn
scripts.build:13:fontawesome-brands: tini ui icon @tinijs/fontawesome-brands-icons @/Font-Awesome-6.4.0/brands && parcel build build/@tinijs/fontawesome-brands-icons/*.bundle.ts --dist-dir build/@tinijs/fontawesome-brands-icons --no-cache --no-source-maps --log-level warn
scripts.build:14:fontawesome-regular: tini ui icon @tinijs/fontawesome-regular-icons @/Font-Awesome-6.4.0/regular && parcel build build/@tinijs/fontawesome-regular-icons/*.bundle.ts --dist-dir build/@tinijs/fontawesome-regular-icons --no-cache --no-source-maps --log-level warn
scripts.build:15:fontawesome-solid: tini ui icon @tinijs/fontawesome-solid-icons @/Font-Awesome-6.4.0/solid && parcel build build/@tinijs/fontawesome-solid-icons/*.bundle.ts --dist-dir build/@tinijs/fontawesome-solid-icons --no-cache --no-source-maps --log-level warn
